/description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Nio96qU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Larsozzo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Return of the Meme: 1222 (duck mathematics)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/MKVb4Br</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mTdI5Wn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's a morning!  Let's get this bread and dress fancy I guess.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UUll7S2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/71Wx09N.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/InhSvio.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/T3EbRwK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I'd like to see a horror movie set on the steppes.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UvGfwlA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oS1w5pN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ujWNpND.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8wEJjQH.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I'd watch this show.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FBgUE31.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/C6JKlRE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Oh, Catullus.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nmK5XEN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The Nika Riots were not a fun time for Justinian.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wM6jHoA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Just Tenochtítlan things.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/W5dgHEe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QgJhZpi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jUl24ZE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RRvTaf4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nebulizer on the Thagomizer</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QZavrQC.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5ypqxw9.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jSVzRIF.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6Jgi49P.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/M4W3MVo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e0vDT3E.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Rise, my friends.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PeEVyKt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RCKwmpn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9rd1sB7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/r2Fhfgx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/paW6I0t.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IulXk8m.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PTXlZM1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kIdvBbK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I had a dream last night where a baby queer person running from their church and oppressive parents moved into the apartment next door, and I became an accidental mentor.  "There are as many gender options and sexualities for you to choose as there are stars in the Sky, and all are valid except for the ones where you're an asshole," I said to them.  

Then one day, they came for her and the rest of the dream was very much reminiscent of the moment Kaveh rose up in Revolt against the Demon king Zahak in the Shahnameh: down to me hoisting one of my wizard robes onto a spear and making it a standard, and I marched out to rescue her with other queer and allied people I know, (including @Ronelyn and @kirbyvictorious) to get them back.  

Wild shit.  Clearly, I should not have had thar late night coffee.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zmOyOzi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fIIs8SP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ppg0TIb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I don't need another sword, but I want another sword.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qrNflKC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My grandmother said something like this to me about one of my historical interests.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gRueB2I.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Stupid Edward Gibbon, Byzantine Empire Hater.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ltUHFuu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FvSuc5t.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nighthawks in the Nighthawks painting.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/glTAZb6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Xl3bWDR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HvDqkHS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is why my doormat says "Go Away" in Sumerian Cunaeform.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/InITNP9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pzTJBFA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1ulDOmh.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ijV0Pbc.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/seWVsaB.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tTh78YP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hahahaha</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/85qHyCT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7TB8SAj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Pippin tax!

Today's message from Pippin: "Glory Pippin!  I love you."</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/f0QuSOo.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/MKVb4Br</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CodyBurkett]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Snowball fight</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/S3BVCty</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e0Ili54.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Also, how many balls do I have to play with to get the extra special trophy?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1MbFaK5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Team acorn pupper tax</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/S3BVCty</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Affaltar]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I bet you can't even throw 5 snowballs....</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Rnjj5Od</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/76UH4e7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>See....typical team Pinecone...</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Rnjj5Od</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Ididntcomehereforthis]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>TEAM ACOOOOORNNNN!!!!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/kxIz7rt</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YE8ocOT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I came a here a minute ago so I don't know what this is about but CRUSH TEAM PINECONE</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/kxIz7rt</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[insanitycontinuum]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Husky taking a Snow Nap</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/EdEcuaI</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uoc2EyH.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><